title: 이달의소녀탐구 #75 (LOONA TV #75)
summary:
0:03 -- The girls are filming near Christmas Time 🎄 but HaSeul almost forgot that it was
Christmas.
0:06 -- She also realizes that some local fans are envious of all of them as they are
filming abroad all the time but it isn’t a journey and they are doing their work.
0:15 -- HaSeul: “We really can’t do anything… Just work and sleep. That’s all.”
0:30 -- The girls are sleeping as they travel. YeoJin: “All my sisters are sleeping~!” and
she sleeps as well.
